    rect rgb(255, 247, 237)
    Note over Test,RB: Current behavior: deployment readiness and binding health converge through separate status streams.
    WSC->>Work: Record Deployment Health=Unhealthy (03:10:27.444)
    WSC->>Work: Record Deployment Health=Healthy (03:10:28.914)
    Work-)RBSC: Work status update enqueues binding reconcile
    RBSC->>RB: Update AggregatedStatus (03:10:29.257)
    RBSC->>RBSC: Reconcile again (03:10:29.963)
    Deploy-->>Test: Replicas are ready (status updated 03:10:29.961)
    Test->>RB: Single GET (03:10:30.035)
    RB-->>Test: Applied=true, Health=Unhealthy
    Test-xTest: Fail immediately
    RBSC->>RB: Complete a later AggregatedStatus update (03:10:30.872)
    Note over RBSC,RB: The recovery update arrives after the terminal assertion.<br/>The artifact does not snapshot its final health value.
    end

    rect rgb(240, 253, 244)
