    Deploy-->>Test: Replicas are ready
    loop Bounded by the existing PollTimeout
        Test->>RB: GET ResourceBinding
        RB-->>Test: Current AggregatedStatus
    end
    RB-->>Test: Applied=true and Health=Healthy
    Test->>Test: Continue migration assertions
